Sean McCabe was diagnosed with stage four Hodgkin Lymphoma in June 2013 . 
  He was told he had just two months to live and planned his own funeral . 
  The father-of-three even wrote a letter to his children to be read to them after he died . 
  He booked the church for his wedding to fiancee Lisa Williams . 
  But in December 2014 he was told his cancer was in remission . 
  He has now rebooked the church and is due to marry Miss Williams in July . 
 